%% seq_04_review.mmd
%% Updated 2026-05-18.
%% Scope: Submit review only.
%% Backend refs:
%%   - GET /reviews/:id
%%   - POST /reviews/:id/submit
%%   - SubmitSkillReviewCommand
%%   - review:submitted listener triggers anomaly detection

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Reviewer as Manager / Peer
    participant B as Browser
    participant C as Controller
    participant Cmd as SubmitSkillReviewCommand
    participant Repo as ReviewRepository
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Listener as review_listener
    participant Anomaly as DetectAnomalyCommand

    Reviewer->>B: Open review form
    B->>C: GET /reviews/:id
    C->>Repo: find session + skills
    Repo->>DB: SELECT review session data
    DB-->>Repo: Session + skills
    Repo-->>C: Response DTO
    C-->>B: Render review form

    Reviewer->>B: Submit skill ratings
    B->>C: POST /reviews/:id/submit
    C->>Cmd: handle(dto)
    Cmd->>Cmd: Validate via ReviewPolicy (pure functions)
    Cmd->>Repo: persist skill reviews
    Repo->>DB: INSERT skill_reviews
    Cmd->>Repo: update session counters/status
    Repo->>DB: UPDATE review_sessions
    Cmd-->>Listener: emit review:submitted
    Listener->>Listener: Invalidate skill/spider cache
    Listener->>Anomaly: Run DetectAnomalyCommand
    Anomaly->>Anomaly: Check fraud patterns
    C-->>B: Redirect with success flash
